# ChangeLog for media-fonts/hanazono-mincho
# Copyright 1999-2015 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: $

  29 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> hanazono-mincho-20141012.ebuild:
  media-fonts/*: fix ${DOCS} to change array to list

   Because font.eclass doesn't support ${DOCS} as array,
  they are fixed to space delimited lists.

   FYI: https://devmanual.gentoo.org/eclass-reference/font.eclass/index.html

  25 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> hanazono-mincho-20141012.ebuild:
  media-fonts/*: Add "mirror" to ${RESTRICT}

   Because they are not uploaded in GENTOO_MIRRORS.

  08 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> hanazono-mincho-20141012.ebuild:
  Update $SRC_URIs and $HOMEPAGEs from sourceforge.jp to osdn.jp

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> hanazono-mincho-20141012.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

*hanazono-mincho-20141012 (04 Jun 2015)

  04 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +hanazono-mincho-20141012.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  Add newly.

     "This font is a free kanji font. The KAGE system, Clipper, FontForge
    and TTX are used to create this font. All glyphs in this font are from
    GlyphWiki."
     http://fonts.jp/hanazono/

